title: Bonus Episode - Khalil Rountree Jr. On Conor McGregor + His Inspirational Journey
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
MMA fighter Khalil Rountree JR sits down with Ebro in the Morning to discuss his inspirational journey including details that his dad used to do security and work with Muhammad Ali, and also worked with Boyz II Men, and his tragic passing. He also spoke about how he prepares for a fight, Conor McGregor's words for him, how he got himself into shape, and much more!
